.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19104106/handup-kids-mtb-gloves-shredder-stoked-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19104106/handup-kids-mtb-gloves-shredder-stoked-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19104106/handup-kids-mtb-gloves-shredder-stoked-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19104106/handup-kids-mtb-gloves-shredder-stoked-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19104106/handup-kids-mtb-gloves-shredder-stoked-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19104106/handup-kids-mtb-gloves-shredder-stoked-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19104106/handup-kids-mtb-gloves-shredder-stoked-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-259297\">The HandUp Kids MTB gloves feature silicone printed graphics on the palm and fingers for extra grip on muddy handlebars</figcaption></figure><p>HandUp have added kids mountain biking gloves with some super fun designs for your stoked little shredders. These are made from a 4-Way stretch fabric with a light mesh on the back of the hand. They get a thin but durable clarino palm and an under wrist velcro strap for a secure fit. There’s also towel-like sweat cloth on the thumb to wipe away the boogies and sweat. Pick the Poncho II and Wild Tie gloves in youth sizes XS-L <a href=\"https://handupgloves.com/collections/youth-gloves\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">for $24.99</a> a pop. You can get these colorways in adult sizing too (along with 10 other designs) <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08XZW47PF/?tag=20br-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">for $29</a>.</p><p>If you’re after something a bit more unique, it’s worth taking a look at the limited edition Strong Life HandUp Gloves, designed by artist and Hopi tribe member, Duane Koyawena. From the artist himself:</p><figure id=\"attachment_259298\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-259298\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves.jpg\" alt=\"handup strong life limited edition gloves\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19105924/HandUp-Strong-Life-limited-edition-gloves-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-259298\">The HandUp Strong Life Gloves are selling fast, now only available in sizes XXS-M for $29 – proceeds go to the <a href=\"https://www.hopieducationfund.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hopi Education Endowment Fund</a></figcaption></figure><p><em>“The images depicted in this design represent important values held by Hopi people. The band across the center features Hopi pottery designs, the colors selected are representative of traditional pigments, and the dashes and waves are symbolic of moisture and rain for the lands. The centered parallel white lines (II) denote strength, and the sun design represents the reverence we have for Tawa, the sun. These elements all together symbolize a commitment to our traditions and our dedication to hard work for a good life”.</em></p><p><em>“This design was inspired by the challenge and joy I get from mountain biking. It has been a good way for me to get out and spend time with my daughter and friends. This design for me brings together my ideas of wellness, health, and my appreciation of the land”.</em></p><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wBxmovB1U-c?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></span></p><p>As of Spring 2021, all HandUp Gloves are touch-screen compatible.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19111505/2021-handup-shorties-short-finger-cycling-gloves.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19111505/2021-handup-shorties-short-finger-cycling-gloves.jpg\" alt=\"2021 handup short finger gloves\" width=\"1200\" height=\"674\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19111505/2021-handup-shorties-short-finger-cycling-gloves.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19111505/2021-handup-shorties-short-finger-cycling-gloves-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/191115