oves-768x431.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19111505/2021-handup-shorties-short-finger-cycling-gloves-696x391.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19111505/2021-handup-shorties-short-finger-cycling-gloves-1068x600.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19111505/2021-handup-shorties-short-finger-cycling-gloves-748x420.jpg 748w\"></a></p><p>Finally, we get to the <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08Y675TXY/?tag=20br-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HandUp short finger cycling gloves</a>, purpose built for riding all day on road or gravel. These are packed with some neat features; stretch-cuff, nylon-reinforced upper, clarino leather palm, pull tabs underneath the fingers, laser-cut ventilation holes, stress-relief gussets on the outboard edge, silicone printed graphics and a towel-like sweat cloth on the thumb. Pick them up <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08Y675TXY/?tag=20br-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">for $24</a>.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19111958/handup-short-finger-cycling-gloves-stoked.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19111958/handup-short-finger-cycling-gloves-stoked.jpg\" alt=\"handup short fimger gloves clarino leather palm\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19111958/handup-short-finger-cycling-gloves-stoked.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19111958/handup-short-finger-cycling-gloves-stoked-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19111958