-padded-womens-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19112856/bionic-half-finger-cycling-gloves-padded-womens-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19112856/bionic-half-finger-cycling-gloves-padded-womens-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19112856/bionic-half-finger-cycling-gloves-padded-womens-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a>The padding is said to result in a relaxed grip with some shock absorption helping to reduce the vibrations transferred to the rider. They also get some reflective strips on the back of the hand to help you be seen by other road users.&nbsp;Bionic Cycling Gloves are sold for $44.99.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.bionicgloves.com/all-products/cycling\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>BionicGloves.com</em></a></p><h2>Lizard Skins Long and Short Finger Gloves</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves.jpg\" alt=\"lizard skins monitor cycling gloves long finger\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19113907/lizard-skins-monitor-cycling-gloves-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Lizard Skins, better known for their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/05/03/lizard-skins-dsp-v2-bar-tape-fattens-up-with-new-4-6mm-thickness-in-four-colors/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">handlebar tape</a>, have released six new cycling gloves; three long finger options and three short finger options. The Monitor line are their long finger cycling gloves. The <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B094MRRB8V/?tag=20br-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ignite model ($27.99)</a> is the lightweight option designed for unrestricted flexibility. These have a one-piece single-layer thin palm.</p><p>The <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B094MX3KYR/?tag=20br-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Monitor Traverse ($29.99)</a> has a three-panel palm with added gel pads. The <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B094MVG6PD/?tag=20br-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">OPS model ($27.99)</a> is the most durable of the three featuring added protection at the knuckles. This one has a one piece suede palm.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves.jpg\" alt=\"lizard skins aramus short finger gloves\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19115722/lizard-skins-aramis-short-finger-gloves-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The Lizard Skins Aramus line of short finger road cycling gloves feature an over wrist velcro strap, inter-finger pulls to make taking them off easier, and microfibre nose wipes. The <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B094Q7FKGF/?tag=20br-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">$22.99 Apex model</a> gets a suede three-panel palm with padding to dampen vibrations. The <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B094Q3WFB6/?tag=20br-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">$31.99 Cadence model</a> features gel padding to enhance that damping effect. The top-of-the-line Classic glove <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01N78X65M/?tag=20br-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">retails at $39.99</a> and gets gel padding with a perforated leather back panel and leather palm.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.lizardskins.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>LizardSkins.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"d41697730296ab6cd74e1b2ace6c99e725854e8895bae037eec5f4f3a1ad440f","category":"Cycling"}